name: Seafood
description: Dive into an ocean of flavors, where each bite of seafood is a harmonious blend of freshness and indulgence, a celebration of the finest treasures from the deep blue.

name: Lamb
description: Embark on a journey of tender elegance, where every cut of lamb is a bold statement of rich flavors, and each bite tells a story of sophisticated culinary mastery.

name: Starter
description: Begin your meal with a burst of creativity, where every starter is a delicate balance of flavors, setting the perfect tone for a truly unforgettable dining experience.

name: Chicken
description: Discover the perfect harmony in every piece of chicken, where each dish is a timeless combination of tenderness and flavor, a classic favorite elevated to new heights.

name: Beef
description: Savor the artistry in every cut of beef, where each bite brings you closer to a masterpiece of savory indulgence, showcasing the richness and depth of the finest meats.

name: Desserts
description: Go on a taste journey, where every sip is a sophisticated creative chord, and every dessert is an expression of the most refined gastronomic desires.

name: Vegan
description: Experience the pure joy of plant-based perfection, where each vegan dish is a vibrant celebration of fresh ingredients and flavors, offering a healthier yet equally indulgent alternative.

name: Pork
description: Delight in the juicy tenderness of pork, where each bite is a fusion of savory richness and subtle sweetness, delivering an unforgettable experience for the senses.

name: Vegetarian
description: Immerse yourself in a world of vibrant, wholesome flavors, where every vegetarian dish is an inspiring expression of nature's bounty, thoughtfully crafted for your enjoyment.

name: Miscellaneous
description: Step into a world of culinary surprises, where each dish in this category offers an eclectic mix of ingredients and flavors, challenging the norms and inviting you to explore the unexpected.

name: Pasta
description: Indulge in a pasta adventure, where every twist and turn is an ode to Italy's finest traditions, bringing together the freshest ingredients for a delightful taste experience.

name: Breakfast
description: Begin your day with an extraordinary breakfast, where every bite is a warm embrace, bringing together comfort and creativity to fuel your morning with delicious energy.

name: Side
description: Complement your main course with sides that are more than just an accompaniment, where every dish is crafted to elevate the meal, adding a perfect balance of flavor and texture.

name: Goat
description: Experience the bold and distinctive flavors of goat, where each dish showcases the unique tenderness and richness of this exquisite meat, crafted to tantalize the taste buds.

name: Soup
description: Warm your soul with every spoonful of soup, where each bowl is a comforting blend of flavors, carefully crafted to nourish and delight, bringing warmth to any moment.
